data.description: Come see this great family home that backs to a nice commons area for plenty of outside activities. Home features 3 bedrooms, plus 3 bath areas, a double stall garage & 3 different family rooms (one could be used as a formal dining room). Heating & Air 2017, newer main level flooring, upstairs carpet new last month, water heater 2021, roof, all new windows, siding, soffits, fascia, gutters all new. Also, this home is close to all schools, shopping, park, and a bike path. Call today to schedule your private showing.
